INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2011-07-06 03:56:25','2011-07-06 03:56:25','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2011-07-06 03:56:25','2011-07-06 03:56:25','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(3,1,'2011-07-06 03:56:38','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2011-07-06 03:56:38','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=3',0,'post','',0),(5,1,'2011-04-06 12:36:00','2011-04-06 12:36:00','The ADF&G is predicting a very large King Salmon run this year and have extablished new regulations for the 2011 Season.\n\nFor May, non-resident anglers can catch 2 Kings per day and keep an annual limit of 5 Kings\n\nFor June through September, non-resident anglers can catch 1 King per day, but also keep an annual limit of 5 Kings.\n\nThis is great news for Talon Lodge guests.  If history repeats itself, a strong King Salmon run will also bring a strong Silver (Coho) Salmon run.\n\nLet\'s hope for the best!','Great Salmon Season Predicted','','publish','open','open','','great-salmon-season-predicted','','','2011-04-06 12:36:00','2011-04-06 12:36:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=5',0,'post','',0),(6,1,'2011-02-26 17:03:00','2011-02-26 17:03:00','We had a great time with our Chefs last week as we planned out our menu for the 2011 Season.  \n\nI have to tell you - this is going to be a GREAT menu and a lot of fun when it comes to paring wine.\n\nCheck out this Salmon dish: Seared Alaska King Salmon with Orzo Pasta, Pine Nuts, Basil & Sauce Putanesca','2011 Menu Planning','','publish','open','open','','2011-menu-planning','','','2011-02-26 17:03:00','2011-02-26 17:03:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=6',0,'post','',0),(7,1,'2010-10-19 09:55:00','2010-10-19 09:55:00','<p>Our Visiting Chef Series and Visiting Winemaker Series events have become the most sought after events in Alaska!&nbsp; </p>\n<p>We have secured the following chefs and winemakers for the 2011 season:</p>\n<p>May 26-30 and May 30-June 3 - Venge Vineyards with Kirk Venge</p>\n<p>June 3-7 and June 7-11 - Chef Sam Choy</p>\n<p>July 2-6 and July 6-10 - Chef John Ash</p>\n<p>July 14-18 and July 18-22&nbsp; - B-Cellars</p>\n<p>July 22-26 and July 26-30 - Chef Pascal Vignau</p>\n<p>August 7-11 and 11-15 - Saddleback Cellars with Nils Venge</p>\n<p>Only 16 guests per event.&nbsp; You will want to secure your space as soon as possible.</p>','Visiting Chef Series and Visiting Winemaker Series Set','','publish','open','open','','visiting-chef-series-and-visiting-winemaker-series-set','','','2010-10-19 09:55:00','2010-10-19 09:55:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=7',0,'post','',0),(8,1,'2010-10-18 17:12:00','2010-10-18 17:12:00','<p><img title=\"Salmon Sushi at Talon Lodge\" height=824 alt=Salmon_Sushi.jpg src=\"/pt/uploads/_MG_0046.jpg\" width=550 border=0></p>\n<p>Guests enjoyed fresh Salmon Sushi at Talon Lodge</p>','2010 Season Photos','','publish','open','open','','2010-season-photos','','','2010-10-18 17:12:00','2010-10-18 17:12:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=8',0,'post','',0),(9,1,'2010-10-18 17:04:00','2010-10-18 17:04:00','<p><img title=\"311 LB Halibut\" height=404 alt=311LB_Halibut.jpg src=\"/pt/uploads/311LB_Halibut.jpg\" width=550 border=0></p>\n<p>Captain Cole and First Mate Andrew sand next to this great 311LB halibut caught during the 2010 season.</p>','2010 season photos','','publish','open','open','','2010-season-photos-2','','','2010-10-18 17:04:00','2010-10-18 17:04:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=9',0,'post','',0),(10,1,'2009-12-10 08:13:00','2009-12-10 08:13:00','<p>Talon Lodge is now on Facebook and we encourage you to become a Fan.</p>\n<p>Our facebook page is being updates on a regular basis with photos, videos and stories from our guests.&nbsp; We are also posting our special events and our summer schedule, and posting this information on Facebook as well as on our blog.</p>\n<p>You can become a fan by clicking this link <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/#/pages/Talon-Lodge-and-Spa-Alaska-Fishing-Lodge/48805291363?ref=ts\">Talon Lodge Facebook</a></p>','Alaska Fishing Lodge on Facebook','','publish','open','open','','alaska-fishing-lodge-on-facebook','','','2009-12-10 08:13:00','2009-12-10 08:13:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=10',0,'post','',0),(11,1,'2009-07-24 18:11:00','2009-07-24 18:11:00','<p><img height=1 src=\"/WebResource.axd?d=yxsLeMxF-Oo7uFz8YInFGrY1yfstua589OQTqgw-gdFD60nioTdyVRDRs3prcnSw8fIkCjZrNJz6GM6EllcVXWSseolFoUdVyl3a-KnfzGQ1&amp;t=632827296000000000\" width=1><img height=358 alt=Sonia-King-Salmon.jpg src=\"/pt/uploads/Sonia-King-Salmon.jpg\" width=550 border=0></p>\n<p><img height=1 src=\"/WebResource.axd?d=yxsLeMxF-Oo7uFz8YInFGrY1yfstua589OQTqgw-gdFD60nioTdyVRDRs3prcnSw8fIkCjZrNJz6GM6EllcVXWSseolFoUdVyl3a-KnfzGQ1&amp;t=632827296000000000\" width=1>Sonia Visser had the fishing day of a lifetime.&nbsp; Check out this 38lb Alaska King.&nbsp; More importantly, check out the smile!&nbsp; Good job Sonia.</p>','Sonia\'s 38lb Alaska King Salmon','','publish','open','open','','sonias-38lb-alaska-king-salmon','','','2009-07-24 18:11:00','2009-07-24 18:11:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=11',0,'post','',0),(12,1,'2009-06-09 20:40:00','2009-06-09 20:40:00','<p><img title=\"Alaska King Salmon\" height=450 alt=Phill_Dom_Tess_King_Salmon.jpg src=\"/pt/uploads/Phill_Dom_Tess_King_Salmon.jpg\" width=550 border=0></p>\n<p>Phillip Frasch, his son Dominic and Daughter Tessa had a great time on the water and the Kings were biting.&nbsp; Dominic took the prize today, with his 28LB King, but Tessa is determined to take the prize tomorrow.</p>\n<p>We\'re always having fun at Talon Lodge!</p>','Frasch Family Kings','','publish','open','open','','frasch-family-kings','','','2009-06-09 20:40:00','2009-06-09 20:40:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=12',0,'post','',0),(13,1,'2009-05-24 12:00:00','2009-05-24 12:00:00','<p><img title=\"Ince Girls Steelhead Fishing at Talon Lodge\" height=125 alt=Ince-Girls-Steelhead-Fishing.jpg src=\"/pt/uploads/Ince-Girls-Steelhead-Fishing.jpg\" width=550 border=0></p>\n<p>When Nancy Ince decided to take her daughters, Nichole and Samantha,&nbsp;on a \"Girls Trip\" to Talon Lodge, she never imagined that fishing in Alaska would be this much fun!</p>\n<p>While on their wild steelhead trip, yesterday, they took a float plane and had a birds-eye-view of the spectacular Tongass National Forest.</p>\n<p>Once they got to the stream - steelhead were everywhere and they had the time of their lives as they hooked a lot and landed a few.&nbsp; That\'s steelhead fishing!</p>','Ince Girls Strike Steelhead at Talon Lodge','','publish','open','open','','ince-girls-strike-steelhead-at-talon-lodge','','','2009-05-24 12:00:00','2009-05-24 12:00:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=13',0,'post','',0),(14,1,'2009-05-19 13:02:00','2009-05-19 13:02:00','<p><img title=\"Whale Watching At Talon Lodge\" height=125 alt=\"Talon Lodge Whale Watching.jpg\" src=\"/pt/uploads/Talon%20Lodge%20Whale%20Watching.jpg\" width=550 border=0></p>\n<p>On Sunday, May 17, 2009 a group of our guides and staff went out for some early Alaska King Salmon fishing.&nbsp; What they caught was more than a King Salmon!</p>\n<p>Mike Radwanski, our chief mechanic, took this series of photos from one of our fishing boats.&nbsp; These shots are so spectacular that I just had to share them.</p>\n<p>During our daily fishing trips, we cruise through the the heart of some of Alaska\'s best whale watching waters.&nbsp; At Talon Lodge, you get a lot more that just great Alaska fishing!</p>','Simply Spectacular - More than an Alaska Fishing Lodge','','publish','open','open','','simply-spectacular-more-than-an-alaska-fishing-lodge','','','2009-05-19 13:02:00','2009-05-19 13:02:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=14',0,'post','',0),(15,1,'2009-04-13 19:05:00','2009-04-13 19:05:00','<p class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><font face=Calibri>Recently we attended our first sports trade shows in Long Beach and Del Mar.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>While attending these shows I was able to review some of the other <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com\">Alaska lodges</a> and outfitters in Alaska and BC.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Some of what I reviewed astonished me.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Let me explain.</font></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><font face=Calibri>Alaska and BC are very difficult places to research and understand if you are planning a fishing trip or vacation.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>There are hundreds of travel options with a host of facilities that call themselves “<a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/accommodations\">Alaska lodges</a>”.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></font></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><font face=Calibri>On the internet they all show fish and show you photos of what you want to see.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>The truth is, there are vast differences, but it’s hard to pull the truth out of what is being presented.</font></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><font face=Calibri>At the trade shows, I expected to see a more realistic view of what each lodge really offered and expected to see some examples of the truth.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Boy was I wrong!<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Some of the booths and displays were elaborate and provided a complete distortion of the real physical offing and the service offering.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>In fact, some of the booth displays were nicer than the actual facilities being sold. I found myself being embarrassed for the industry and feeling sorry for the consumer.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></font></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><font face=Calibri>There were some (very few) reputable companies who not only represented themselves correctly, but delivered a quality presentation while representing their lodge in a truthful manner.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>One lodge in particular was Kingfisher Charters in Sitka.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Kingfisher is a fine operation and is one of the larger outfitters in the Sitka area.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Kingfisher’s booth presented exactly what Kingfisher offers – this is how it’s supposed to be.</font></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><font face=Calibri>Unfortunately, there were so many other <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/difference\">Alaska fishing lodges</a> that flat out misrepresented their offering and services.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>And in the end, the visitor to these properties is the real loser.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Fortunately, Alaska by itself provides an experience of a lifetime.</font></p>','Alaska Fishing Lodges, there is a difference','','publish','open','open','','alaska-fishing-lodges-there-is-a-difference','','','2009-04-13 19:05:00','2009-04-13 19:05:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=15',0,'post','',0),(16,1,'2009-04-07 07:20:00','2009-04-07 07:20:00','<p><img height=358 alt=Scallops.jpg src=\"/pt/uploads/Scallops.jpg\" width=550 border=0></p>\n<p><font face=Arial>There is a lot of satisfaction and pride that goes into sharing Talon Lodge with our guests.&nbsp; There is also a lot of fun as well!</font></p>\n<p><font face=Arial>Each April, we put the finishing touches on our menu for the upcoming season.&nbsp; This also entails the \"tasting\" of each menu item to ensure that the culinary standards of Talon Lodge are upheld.</font></p>\n<p><font face=Arial>I am pleased to report that after a net weight gain of about 3 pounds, we have pulled together another assortment of culinary delights to share with our guests. Highlighted by <u>Lemon-and-olive-oil poached Alaska King Salmon with caviar lentils and a red wine syrup</u>, and <u>Seared Alaska Halibut with oven-dried tomato risotto and parmesan sauce</u>, the 2009 menu is simply spectacular.</font></p>\n<p><font face=Arial>Now all we have to do is wait for May 23rd to share the menu with our guests.</font></p>','The menu is ready for our 2009 guests','','publish','open','open','','the-menu-is-ready-for-our-2009-guests','','','2009-04-07 07:20:00','2009-04-07 07:20:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=16',0,'post','',0),(17,1,'2009-04-04 05:26:00','2009-04-04 05:26:00','<p><img height=358 alt=whale-jumping-for-joy.jpg src=\"/pt/uploads/whale-jumping-for-joy.jpg\" width=550 border=0></p>\n<p>There is something magical about Alaska!</p>\n<p>I can\'t think of any other place on earth where there is so much majesty and so much wow...&nbsp; There is so much beauty and nature is putting on a show almost everywhere you look.&nbsp; We are fortunate to have this <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/about\">Alaska lodge</a> so that we can experience these wonders first hand and share them with our guests.</p>\n<p>Last week, our friend and Island caretaker, Tim Shobe took this photo on his way to Sitka from <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com\">Talon Lodge</a>.&nbsp; During the herring spawn, each spring, the whales come in close to Sitka to feed.&nbsp; The activity and wonder of it is spectacular.&nbsp; </p>\n<p>You just have to see it for yourself!</p>','The wonder of Alaska!','','publish','open','open','','the-wonder-of-alaska','','','2009-04-04 05:26:00','2009-04-04 05:26:00','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=17',0,'post','',0),(18,4,'2011-09-02 06:39:26','2011-09-02 06:39:26','<p>The Talon Lodge in Sitka is one of a kind! We did not know what to expect of our deep sea fishing adventure and the experience exceeded our expectations! Not only is it a beautiful part of the world, the level of service, attention to detail, the amazing food, friendly staff and family environment left us longing to stay! The fishing was a &quot;hook&quot; and, when coupled with spa amentities, elegant cuisine, and beautiful wines ~ we have recommended it to our friends and family and know we will return! Book your stay now ~ this little gem will not be a secret for long!</p> <p>Stayed May 2011, traveled with family</p>\n<p>Rated 5 out of 5 stars</p>\n<p><a href=\'http://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g60966-d1553334-r117515611-Talon_Lodge_Spa-Sitka_Alaska.html\'>Reviewed on Trip Advisor at 8/1/11</a></p>\n<p>Reviewed by <a href=\'http://www.tripadvisor.com/members/SheSheLaaLaa\'>SheSheLaaLaa</a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a>&nbsp;is a luxury fishing lodge located in Sitka, Alaska. For more information about us or to make a reservation, visit our website or call&nbsp;(888) 763-5630&nbsp;today!</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Reviews\'>Talon Lodge Reviews</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/review/220969/talon-lodge-5-star-review--an-amazing-adventure!--888-763-5630.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','Talon Lodge 5 Star Review | &quot;An Amazing Adventure!&quot; | 888-763-5630','The Talon Lodge in Sitka is one of a kind! We did not know what to expect of our deep sea fishing adventure and the experience exceeded our expectations! Not only is it a beautiful part of the world, the level of service, attention to detail, the amazi...','publish','open','open','','talon-lodge-5-star-review-an-amazing-adventure-888-763-5630-2','','','2011-09-02 06:39:26','2011-09-02 06:39:26','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=18',0,'post','',0),(19,4,'2011-08-17 20:31:45','2011-08-17 20:31:45','<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/206867/medium/206867.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n</p><p>Is fly fishing your greatest passion? If so, this iPhone app from Green Mountain Digital was made for you!</p> <p>If you want to save yourself the time and energy of visiting bait and tackle shops in order to learn from the experts, download <a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id380322999\"  title=\"Orvis Fly Fishing App\">Orvis Fly Fishing</a> today. Animated demonstrations show you how to tie more than twenty different types of fly fishing knots. Experienced fly fishermen and women offer up their best tips for casting flies. Truel Myers, head fly fishing instructor at Orvis, explains the ten most common fly casting mistakes so that you can be sure to avoid them.</p> <p>If you would like to participate in the fly fishing adventure of a lifetime, check out <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a> in Sitka today. <a href=\"http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/contact\"  title=\"Contact Talon Lodge\">Contact us</a> at (888) 763-5630 to find out more about our luxurious resort and hassle-free Alaska fishing trips!</p>\n<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/206872/medium/206872.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/206873/medium/206873.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/206874/medium/206874.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/206875/medium/206875.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/206876/medium/206876.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Fly+Fishing\'>Fly Fishing</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/App\'>App</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Fly+Sishing\'>Fly Sishing</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/206850/2011/08/18/app-orvis-fly-fishing%E2%80%94the-ultimate-fly-fishing-guide.html#comments\'>0 comments</a> | <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/206850/2011/08/18/app-orvis-fly-fishing%E2%80%94the-ultimate-fly-fishing-guide.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','App: Orvis Fly Fishing—The Ultimate Fly Fishing Guide','\n\nIs fly fishing your greatest passion? If so, this iPhone app from Green Mountain Digital was made for you! If you want to save yourself the time and energy of visiting bait and tackle shops in order to learn from 