ass=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Lodge\'>Alaska Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Sitka\'>Alaska Fishing Sitka</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Alaska\'>Talon Lodge Alaska</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Sitka+Fishing+Lodges\'>Sitka Fishing Lodges</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/170118/2011/07/08/like-our-recent-blog-topics-here-are-more-great-resources-for-you-to-check-out!.html#comments\'>0 comments</a> | <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/170118/2011/07/08/like-our-recent-blog-topics-here-are-more-great-resources-for-you-to-check-out!.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','Like Our Recent Blog Topics? Here Are More Great Resources for You to Check Out!','&nbsp;Would you like to learn more about the topics covered in our recent blog posts? If you are in the process of preparing for your great Alaskan fishing adventure, or you are just curious to find out more about the fish that swim in Alaska&rsquo;s b...','inherit','open','open','','like-our-recent-blog-topics-here-are-more-great-resources-for-you-to-check-out','','','2011-07-08 22:35:45','2011-07-08 22:35:45','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=64',0,'post','',0),(65,3,'2011-06-28 14:33:53','2011-06-28 14:33:53','<p>When an experienced fisher hears &ldquo;Alaska,&rdquo; salmon is usually the first fish that comes to mind. Alaskan salmon are certainly special, but Alaska is home to many species of fish that most fishermen or fisherwomen would be thrilled to catch. Here are just a few examples:</p> <p><strong>Alaskan King Salmon</strong></p> <p>Most fishermen who catch an <a href=\"http://www.fishalaskamagazine.com/fish/king_salmon.htm\"  title=\"Alaskan King Salmon\">Alaskan King Salmon</a> while on a luxury fishing trip to Alaska experience an unparalleled moment of pride. If you stay in an Alaskan fishing lodge near the Sitka Sound, your chances of catching Alaska&rsquo;s state fish are better than they would be anywhere else in the state.</p> <p><strong>Arctic Char</strong></p> <p>Most numerous along Alaska&rsquo;s western coast, this greenish-brown fish can sometimes be spotted in Alaska&rsquo;s southeastern waters. It is not uncommon for arctic char to weigh more than fifteen pounds!</p> <p><strong>Dolly Varden</strong></p> <p>If you are on a <a href=\"http://www.alaskafishingak.com/sitka/sitkafishing.htm\"  title=\"Fishing in Sitka, Alaska\">fishing trip in Southeastern Alaska,</a> you are almost guaranteed to see Dolly Varden, a type of fish that is hardly distinguishable from the arctic char. The Dolly Varden is smaller and lighter, usually with silvery sides.</p> <p><strong>Rainbow Trout</strong></p> <p>A favorite catch among fishermen and foodies alike, rainbow trout can be a struggle to wrestle with&mdash;weighing up to forty pounds&mdash;and a delight to eat. These trout are abundant in the freshwater rivers of Alaska&rsquo;s southeastern coast.</p> <p><strong>Copper Rockfish</strong></p> <p>The Copper Rockfish, with its multi-colored scales and its spiky fins, is one of the most intriguing fish in Alaska. Competitive fishermen and thrill-seekers are intrigued by the rockfish because it is the only venomous sport fish in Alaska. This does not make them inedible. In fact, many individuals who do not care for fishy tastes enjoy the tender white meat of this spiny fish.</p> <p>If you want to rest in style after a day of <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/fishing/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge: Fishing\">luxury fishing</a>, Sitka&rsquo;s <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge Website\">Talon Lodge</a> may be the perfect place for you to stay on your next Alaskan fishing trip. With a full service spa, a full gourmet kitchen, and a range of accommodation options to choose from, this fishing resort has something for everyone. Look through our beautiful <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/gallery/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge Photo Gallery\">photo gallery</a> and then call us today at (888) 763-5630 to book a room!</p>\n<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/163699/medium/163699.PNG?ver=1&gen=1\' /><br />\n</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Sitka\'>Alaska Fishing Sitka</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Alaska\'>Talon Lodge Alaska</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Lodge\'>Alaska Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Sitka+Fishing+Lodges\'>Sitka Fishing Lodges</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/163668/2011/06/28/what-type-of-fish-can-you-catch-in-alaska.html#comments\'>0 comments</a> | <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/163668/2011/06/28/what-type-of-fish-can-you-catch-in-alaska.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','What Type of Fish Can You Catch in Alaska?','When an experienced fisher hears &ldquo;Alaska,&rdquo; salmon i