158449.PNG?ver=1&gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/158450/medium/158450.PNG?ver=1&gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/158451/medium/158451.PNG?ver=1&gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/158452/medium/158452.PNG?ver=1&gen=1\' /><br />\n</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Sitka\'>Alaska Fishing Sitka</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Alaska\'>Talon Lodge Alaska</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Lodge\'>Alaska Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Sitka+Fishing+Lodges\'>Sitka Fishing Lodges</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/158446/2011/06/22/itunes-app-the-alaska-app.html#comments\'>0 comments</a> | <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/158446/2011/06/22/itunes-app-the-alaska-app.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','iTunes App: The Alaska App','\n\nAre you planning a vacation to Alaska? If so, this free app can save you hours of research. With detailed information regarding all of Alaska&rsquo;s best places to visit, including photos or videos for most of them, the Alaska App is useful even to ...','inherit','open','open','','27-revision-4','','','2011-06-22 04:24:03','2011-06-22 04:24:03','',27,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=66',0,'revision','',0),(67,3,'2011-06-13 19:41:40','2011-06-13 19:41:40','<p>Every fisherman dreams of fishing for salmon in Alaska&rsquo;s cool, clean rivers or the Sitka Sound. If you are preparing for the Alaskan fishing trip you have always dreamed of, keep the following <a href=\"http://www.fishabout.com/article/Packing_for_Your_Next_Fishing_Trip\"  title=\"Packing for Your Next Fishing Trip\">packing tips</a> in mind as you prepare to set off for your fishing lodge.</p> <p><strong>Bring waterproof everything.</strong></p> <p>The purpose of your trip is to fish. You are going to get wet, and the water will be cold. Bring at least one or two articles of waterproof clothing, including shoes, to cover every part of your body. Doing this will help you stay warm and dry. Bring extra socks, as cold and wet feet are uncomfortable and increase your risk of frostbite.<strong><br /><br /></strong></p> <p><strong>Service and pack your fishing gear.</strong></p> <p>If any of your fishing gear is in need of maintenance, have it serviced before your Alaska fishing trip. You may also want to bring a small tool kit to make any necessary repairs in the field.</p> <p><strong>Pack enough layers.</strong></p> <p>Days can be cool in Alaska and nights are usually chilly, even in summer. However, the Sitka sun can sometimes make the temperature feel warmer than it actually is in the middle of the day. Plan on wearing easily-removable layers so that you can be comfortable both when you set off early in the morning and during the middle of the day when the sun is at its highest point.</p> <p><strong>Consider your lodgings.</strong></p> <p>Your packing list will be different if you stay at a luxury fishing lodge than it will be if you are camping for two weeks. Think about your lodging when you pack clothes, toiletries, and supplies.</p> <p><strong>Don&rsquo;t forget bug spray!</strong></p> <p>Alaska is a notorious <a href=\"http://www.alaskacenters.gov/pests.cfm\"  title=\"Alaska\'s Pests\">insect haven</a> during the summertime. Be considerate of the environment and bring a pump or cream, as they are more environmentally friendly than aerosol sprays. Depending on where you are sleeping, you may also want to consider packing a mosquito net.</p> <p>To start planning your luxurious Alaska fishing adventure, check out the <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge Website\">Talon Lodge</a>, Sitka&rsquo;s premier fishing resort. Call us at (888) 763-5630 to find out more!</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Sitka\'>Alaska Fishing Sitka</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Alaska\'>Talon Lodge Alaska</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Lodge\'>Alaska Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Sitka+Fishing+Lodges\'>Sitka Fishing Lodges</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/149606/2011/06/15/tips-for-packing-for-your-alaskan-fishing-trip.html#comments\'>0 comments</a> | <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/149606/2011/06/15/tips-for-packing-for-your-alaskan-fishing-trip.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','Tips for Packing for Your Alaskan Fishing Trip','Every fisherman dreams of fishing for salmon in Alaska&rsquo;s cool, clean rivers or the Sitka Sound. If you are preparing for the Alaskan fishing trip you have always dreamed of, keep the following packing tips in mind as you prepare to set off for yo...','inherit','open','open','','28-revision-4','','','20