'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=70',0,'revision','',0),(71,3,'2011-06-01 18:26:55','2011-06-01 18:26:55','<p>Barrow, Alaska, located 330 miles north of the Arctic Circle, is the home of the Inupiat tribe.  During the summer this region sees temperatures peak at about a mere 40 degrees Fahrenheit and experiences more than 80 days of 24-hour sunlight.  Because of the constant sunshine, the town has a curfew that begins at 11 pm to keep children from playing outside at midnight.  Due to the copious snow, most people travel via dog sleds or snowmobiles.  The average household income is $58,000.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>To learn more about this town that&rsquo;s full of unique character watch this video. Book a stay at the <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a> for an authentic Alaskan experience&mdash;it&rsquo;s like nothing you&rsquo;ve ever seen.  Contact us today!</p>\n<p class=\"videos\">\n<a href=\'http://www.youtube.com/v/TEP9y17gMso?hl=en&fs=1\'>http://www.youtube.com/v/TEP9y17gMso?hl=en&fs=1</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Sitka\'>Alaska Fishing Sitka</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Alaska\'>Talon Lodge Alaska</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Sitka+Fishing+Lodges\'>Sitka Fishing Lodges</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/139139/2011/06/02/alaska-lonely-planet-travel-video.html#comments\'>0 comments</a> | <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/139139/2011/06/02/alaska-lonely-planet-travel-video.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','Alaska: Lonely Planet Travel Video','Barrow, Alaska, located 330 miles north of the Arctic Circle, is the home of the Inupiat tribe.  During the summer this region sees temperatures peak at about a mere 40 degrees Fahrenheit and experiences more than 80 days of 24-hour sunlight.  Because ...','inherit','open','open','','32-revision-4','','','2011-06-01 18:26:55','2011-06-01 18:26:55','',32,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=71',0,'revision','',0),(72,3,'2011-05-16 14:52:37','2011-05-16 14:52:37','<p>Alaska has one of the most beautiful and unique natural landscapes in the world. The next time you&rsquo;re on an Alaskan fishing trip, keep your eyes open for these majestic creatures that make up the state&rsquo;s diverse wildlife.</p> <p><strong>Killer Whales</strong></p> <p>The Killer Whale, also known as the Orca, is one of the most famous of all the <a href=\"http://www.fakr.noaa.gov/protectedresources/mmv/guide.htm\"  title=\"Viewing Humpback Whales\">marine mammals</a>. Try to catch sight of these magical creatures as they roll through the waves near your Alaska fishing resort. Watching a whale in its natural habitat is a moving experience, especially if it&rsquo;s a beautiful Orca. The black and white of their bodies slices through the blue/grey waters, giving you a glimpse that will leave you breathless.</p> <p><strong>The Bald Eagle</strong></p> <p>With more than 30,000 bald eagles in the state, Alaska is the perfect place to see this national emblem in person. Watch them in their natural habitats as they fly along the Alaskan waterways. Don&rsquo;t forget to occasionally look toward the sky as you&rsquo;re sitting by the water of your Alaska fishing lodge. Chances are that you&rsquo;ll see a bald eagle swoop through the sky.</p> <p><strong>Grizzly Bears</strong></p> <p>Alaska has 98% of the United States of America&rsquo;s grizzly population living within its borders. Only in Alaska do you have the opportunity to see such <a href=\"http://www.alaskascenes.com/wildlife.html\"  title=\"Wildlife in Alaska\">wildlife</a> in its natural habitat, unspoiled by relocation or other issues that come with building and city development.  Of course, you&rsquo;ll want to keep your distance from these powerful animals.</p> <p><strong>Halibut and Salmon</strong></p> <p>Your luxury fishing in Alaska won&rsquo;t be complete without an opportunity to catch some halibut and salmon in beautiful waters. Ask your fishing guide about the best places to catch these fish.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>Come and see the diverse wildlife of Alaska at the <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/about/wildlife.asp\"  title=\"Talon Lodge: Wildlife\">Talon Lodge.</a> If you want to experience <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/fishing/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge: Fishing\">luxury fishing in Sitka</a> while you enjoy precious wildlife, then we&rsquo;re the place for you.  At Talon Lodge, you can have the best and most relaxing <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/difference/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge: The Difference\">Alaskan fishing trip</a> of your life. Call today to reserve your spot.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/125782/medium/125782.PNG?ver=1&gen=1\' /><br />\n</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Sitka\'>Alaska Fishing Sitka</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Alaska\'>Talon Lodge Alaska</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Lodge\'>Alaska Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Sitka+Fishing+Lodges\'>Sitka Fishing Lodges</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/125783/2011/05/26/a-look-at-alaskas-wildlife.html#comments\'>1 comments</a> | <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/125783/2011/05/26/a-look-at-alaskas-wildlife.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','A Look at Alaska\'s Wildlife','Alaska has one of the most beautiful and unique natural landscapes in the world. The next time you&rsquo;re on an Alaskan fishing trip, keep your eyes open for these majestic creatures that make up the state&rsquo;s diverse wildlife. Killer Whales The ...','inherit','open','open','','35-revision-4','','','2011-05-16 14:52:37','2011-05-16 14:52:37','',35,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=72',0,'revision','',0),(75,4,'2011-09-23 08:11:54','2011-09-23 08:11:54','<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/238452/medium/238452.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n</p><p>Alaska is one of the country&rsquo;s most beautiful and unique states. That&rsquo;s why so many people choose it as their vacation destination. <strong><a href=\"http://www.ehow.com/facts_7272807_do-pack-alaska-vacation_.html\"  title=\"Alaskan Fishing Resorts\">Alaskan fishing resorts</a></strong> can provide the best experience, offering luxury, style, and great outdoor opportunities. If you&rsquo;re planning an Alaskan vacation, then look for these qualities in a resort:</p> <ul> <li><strong>Included Meals</strong></li> </ul> <p>Some fishing resorts are home to stunning restaurants that provide delicious meals&mdash;but at an outrageous price! When looking for a true luxury experience, you should find a resort that includes meals with each guests&rsquo; stay. This feature lets you experience a variety of delectable, top-quality meals for breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Many resorts offer an assortment of gourmet seafood entr&eacute;es, featuring favorites such as salmon, crab, and halibut.</p> <ul> <li><strong>Guided Activities</strong></li> </ul> <p>Many Alaskan visitors want to spend time outdoors during their vacation. Look for a resort that offers guided fishing, hiking, and kayaking tours and activities. Whether you prefer the water or the land, you&rsquo;ll be able to experience a true adventure on your <strong><a href=\"http://www.sitka.net/sitka/culturehistory.html\"  title=\"Alaskan Vacation\">Alaskan vacation</a></strong>.</p> <ul> <li><strong>A Relaxing Atmosphere</strong></li> </ul> <p>After experiencing the outdoors, you&rsquo;ll want to have a comfortable place to rest. You can find this comfort in a resort where guests are treated as a top priority. These resorts offer the best in relaxation, simplicity, and caring treatment. They also offer open, spacious rooms that let you clear your mind and enjoy every moment of your vacation.</p> <ul> <li><strong>An On-Site Spa</strong></li> </ul> <p>Nothing provides more relaxation that a trip to the spa. Some Alaskan fishing resorts offer on-site spas where guests can choose from a variety of styles of massage therapy. The experience is made even more relaxing and serene by the beautiful views all around you.</p> <p>You&rsquo;ll find all of these great features and more at <strong><a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a></strong>. Our luxury Alaskan fishing resort provides everything you need for fun, adventure, and total relaxation. For more information about our resort, visit our website or <strong><a href=\"http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/contact\"  title=\"Contact Talon Lodge\">contact us</a></strong> at (888) 763-5630.</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Fishing\'>Fishing</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Lodge\'>Alaska Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/238451/2011/09/23/what-to-look-for-in-an-alaskan-fishing-resort.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','What to Look for in an Alaskan Fishing Resort','\n\nAlaska is one of the country&rsquo;s most beautiful and unique states. That&rsquo;s why so many people choose it as their vacation destination. Alaskan fishing resorts can provide the best experience, offering luxury, style, and great outdoor opportu...','publish','closed','closed','','what-to-look-for-in-an-alaskan-fishing-resort','','','2011-09-23 08:11:54','2011-09-23 08:11:54','',0,'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/238451/2011/09/23/what-to-look-for-in-an-alaskan-fishing-resort.html',0,'post','',0),(76,4,'2011-09-16 14:36:47','2011-09-16 14:36:47','<p class=\"videos\">\n<a href=\'http://www.youtube.com/v/5yRwf5W_beY?hl=en&fs=1\'>http://www.youtube.com/v/5yRwf5W_beY?hl=en&fs=1</a>\n</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/about/location.asp\"  title=\"Sitka\">Sitka</a></strong> is one of Alaska&rsquo;s most beautiful cities. Sitting on the edge of the Pacific Ocean, it&rsquo;s often called the &ldquo;Paris of the Pacific.&rdquo; Just 800 miles north of Seattle, this wonderful city is home to some of the world&rsquo;s best whale-watching.</p> <p>In this video, you&rsquo;ll get a closer look at the beautiful city of Sitka. Every year, people come from around the world to get amazing views of humpback whales that travel through the waters of Sitka. The mountains extend out to the waters, offering some of the world&rsquo;s most unique views.</p> <p>If you&rsquo;re ready to experience Sitka, then visit us at <strong><a href=\"http://www.talonlodg