,0,'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/220417/2011/09/01/fishing-and-massage-resources-from-talon-lodge.html',0,'post','',0),(80,4,'2011-08-25 05:37:58','2011-08-25 05:37:58','<p>If you&rsquo;ve already made an appointment for a spa massage at your <a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2010/09/21/health/research/21regimens.html\"  title=\"Alaska Luxury Fishing Resort\">luxury fishing resort in Alaska</a>, you are in for a treat! Your body&rsquo;s aches and pains are gently rubbed away by the pampering of a licensed massage therapist.</p> <p><strong>The General Experience</strong></p> <p>Whether or not the massage you are receiving is professionally administered, conducted at a massage parlor, or in the comfort of your own home, you will most likely enjoy it. However, a spa massage is a luxurious experience unlike any other. Sign up for a day at the spa and expect to feel relaxed, relieved, and completely at ease with yourself and the world &ndash; all you need to do is show up!</p> <p><strong>Traditional Swedish Massage</strong></p> <p>The majority of massages performed by certified therapists are Swedish massages, and for good reason. The <a href=\"http://spas.about.com/od/swedishmassage/a/Swedish.htm\"  title=\"Swedish massage\">Swedish massage</a>&mdash;characterized by, flowing strokes&mdash;is the most effective way to therapeutically reduce muscle pain, repair joint stiffness, and increase blood circulation at the same time. If you have osteoarthritis, or have spent the day on a fishing trip in the Alaska cold, or you just feel like being pampered, this massage is perfect for you.</p> <p><strong>The Joys of Hot Stone</strong></p> <p>If you&rsquo;re feeling exceptionally tense after your exciting day of Alaskan fly fishing, a hot stone massage will work wonders for you! In addition to easing muscle stiffness and stress, this massage will increase your circulation and give your metabolism a little boost. During a hot stone massage, you can expect to relax on your front side while a massage therapist strategically places heat retaining stones on your back. The heat from these stones will penetrate deep into your muscle tissue, releasing the tension that has built up during the day, week, or lifetime since your last hot stone massage.</p> <p>How does a luxurious and soothing spa massage on the water&rsquo;s edge in the beautiful woods of Alaska sound to you? When you stay at <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a> in Sitka, you can have all of this and more! Spend your day at the spa, or pay a short 60- or 90-minute visit when you return from your fishing trip. Either way, you won&rsquo;t want to leave. <a href=\"http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/contact\"  title=\"Contact Talon Lodge\">Contact us</a> at (888) 763-5630 to find out more about Alaska&rsquo;s most luxurious fishing resort or <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/spa/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge Spa\">book your spa package today</a>!</p>\n<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/213221/medium/213221.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/213222/medium/213222.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/213223/medium/213223.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/213224/medium/213224.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Spa\'>Spa</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Swedish+Massage\'>Swedish Massage</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Massage\'>Massage</a>, <a href=\'http:/