 information on wine pairings, both with fish and other meals, ...','inherit','open','open','','alaskan-vacation-resources-for-you','','','2011-09-25 23:57:16','2011-09-25 23:57:16','',0,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=81',0,'post','',0),(82,4,'2011-08-10 17:11:38','2011-08-10 17:11:38','<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/200667/medium/200667.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n</p><p>Freshwater fishing in Alaska may be the best fishing of its kind in the world. Even after decades of commercial fishing, the rivers, lakes, and streams of places like Sitka are teeming with salmon, steelhead, and trout. If you&rsquo;re planning on <a href=\"http://www.fishingloft.com/freshwater-fishing-basics.html\"  title=\"Alaska Fishing\">freshwater fishing in Alaska</a>, keep these three important elements in mind.</p> <p><strong>1.&nbsp;</strong><strong>Master the hook, line, and sinker method.</strong></p> <p>One of the most common styles of freshwater fishing is also the easiest for many anglers. If you are a novice, the hook, line, and sinker method is a good place to start. Alaska has many beautiful lakes that make great places to learn, develop, and master the basics of this sport. These lakes are also crowded with fish, increasing your chances of getting a bite and catching a fish on your first outing.</p> <p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>2.&nbsp;</strong><strong>Give Alaskan fly fishing a go.</strong></p> <p>Once you have caught a few fish with your rod, hook, and sinker, you will be ready to try your hand at <a href=\"http://www.alaskaflyfishingonline.com/\"  title=\"Alaska Fishing\">fly fishing</a>, an Alaskan freshwater angler&rsquo;s favorite. This is where fishing gets really exciting, as you wade in the waters of the rivers anglers all over the world dream of, waiting for salmon and trout to jump at the &ldquo;fly&rdquo; at the end of your rod.</p> <p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>3. </strong><strong>When in the company of experts, ask questions.</strong></p> <p>One of the best ways to improve your freshwater fishing skills is to learn from those who fish for a living or have a wealth of fishing experience. There is no better place to do this than Alaska, where fishing is the favorite pastime of many residents. If you take a luxury fishing trip, ask your guide any questions you may have.</p> <p>Are you looking to try some prime <a href=\"http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/contact\"  title=\"Contact Talon Lodge\">Alaska fishing</a>? If you would like to stay in a luxurious resort, enjoy fine dining in the evenings, and spend your days at Alaska&rsquo;s best salmon fishing locations, <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a> in Sitka is perfect for your Alaskan vacation! Visit our website or call us at (888) 763-5630 to <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/reserve/\"  title=\"Make a Reservation at Talon Lodge\">make a reservation</a> today!</p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/200664/2011/08/11/alaskan-freshwater-fishing-fundamentals.html#comments\'>0 comments</a> | <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/200664/2011/08/11/alaskan-freshwater-fishing-fundamentals.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','Alaskan Freshwater Fishing Fundamentals','\n\nFreshwater fishing in Alaska may be the best fishing of its kind in the world. Even after decades of commercial fishing, the rivers, lakes, and streams of places like Sitka are teeming with salmon, steelhead, and trout. If you&rsquo;re planning on fr...','publish','closed','closed','','alaskan-freshwater-fishing-fundamentals','','','2011-08-10 17:11:38','2011-08-10 17:11:38','',0,'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/200664/2011/08/11/alaskan-freshwater-fishing-fundamentals.html',0,'post','',0),(83,4,'2011-11-04 19:51:40','2011-11-04 19:51:40','<p>Hard to believe that we are already planning our 2012 menu.&nbsp; Where