ags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Alaska\'>Talon Lodge Alaska</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Reviews\'>Talon Lodge Reviews</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/review/256321/5-star-review-on-trip-advisor--talon-lodge--888-763-5630.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','5 Star Review on Trip Advisor | Talon Lodge | 888-763-5630','Talon Lodge was an incredible and amazing place. My three sons and father-in-law experienced magnificent service and the accomodations were perfect. The food was tremendous and was only topped by the quality of the service we received every minute we w...','publish','closed','closed','','5-star-review-on-trip-advisor-talon-lodge-888-763-5630','','','2011-10-11 19:16:42','2011-10-11 19:16:42','',0,'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/review/256321/5-star-review-on-trip-advisor--talon-lodge--888-763-5630.html',0,'post','',0),(86,4,'2011-10-07 19:48:52','2011-10-07 19:48:52','<p>When some people think of Alaska, they picture a great expanse of sparsely populated land that is covered in snow and glaciers. When others think about Alaska, they imagine a <a href=\"http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Auk/v015n02/p0122-p0131.pdf\">birdwatcher&rsquo;s paradise</a> where some of the world&rsquo;s rarest and most exotic birds travel in the summertime to feed on an abundance of fish and enjoy the ideal nesting conditions Alaska&rsquo;s forests provide. This guide introduces some of the birds you can expect to see on your next luxury birding tour to southeast Alaska.</p> <p><strong>Where to go:</strong></p> <p><a href=\"http://alaskamaritime.fws.gov/visitors-educators/wildlifeviewing/sitka.htm\">St. Lazaria Island</a>, located just fifteen miles southwest of Sitka, boasts some of the best bird-watching in all of Alaska. The city of Sitka and its surrounding conifer forests are also perfect for bird watching.</p> <p><strong>When to go:</strong></p> <p>The lush and temperate climate in Sitka and the surrounding area means that the bird-watching season in the southeast is a bit longer than in most parts of Alaska. In fact, birds of interest can be spotted on and near St. Lazaria Island all year long. For sightings during breeding or peak migration, however, plan a trip between April and September.</p> <p><strong>What you can expect to see:</strong></p> <ul> <li>Albatross: One of the largest flying birds in the world, the albatross is a bird every birder wishes to spot at one point or another. </li> </ul>\n<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/253208/medium/253208.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n</p><ul> <li>Rhinoceros Auklet: With a horn resembling that of a rhinoceros, this adorable seabird is especially interesting to watch when it is young.</li> <li>Willow Ptarmigan: Easily recognizable by its marbled brown color and thick bill, Alaska&rsquo;s state bird can be seen all year round.</li> <li>Other seabirds: such as the ancient murrelet, shearwater, and storm-petrol are also commonly spotted feeding and migrating near Sitka.</li> </ul> <p>For a luxury vacation in one of Alaska&rsquo;s best birding regions, book a vacation at <a href=\"http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/188933/2011/07/28/how-to-plan-a-week-at-an-alaska-fishing-resort.html\">Talon Lodge</a> in Sitka. Call (888) 763-5630 to find out how to combine your birding endeavors with a first-rate fishing trip, five-star cuisine, and luxurious spa services.</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Birdwatching+Alaska\'>Birdwatching Alaska</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/253204/2011/10/07/a-guide-to-birdwatching-in-alaska.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','A Guide to Birdwatching in Alaska','When some people think of Alaska, they picture a great expanse of sparsely populated land that is covered in snow and glaciers. When others think about Alaska, they imagine a birdwatcher&rsquo;s paradise where some of the world&rsquo;s rarest and most ...','publish','closed','closed','','a-guide-to-birdwatching-in-alaska','','','2011-10-07 19:48:52','2011-10-07 19:48:52','',0,'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/253204/2011/10/07/a-guide-to-birdwatching-in-alaska.html',0,'post','',0),(87,4,'2011-09-29 18:58:03','2011-09-29 18:58:03','<p>Are you planning an Alaskan adventure? Do you want more tips on what to look for in a resort? You can find more helpful information on the following websites. To learn even more, contact <a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge website\">Talon Lodge</a> today at (888) 763-5630!</p> <ul> <li>Visit this page from USAToday.com to learn more about the many <a href=\"http://traveltips.usatoday.com/information-hiking-alaska-10168.html\">hiking opportunities available in Alaska</a></li> </ul> <ul> <li>Take a look at this page from <a href=\"http://www.sitka.org/explore/wildlife/\">Sitka.org</a> for more information about the wildlife you&rsquo;ll experience in Sitka.</li> </ul> <ul> <li>You can find more tips on what to wear during your Alaskan vacation on this page from <a href=\"http://alaska.org/what-to-wear.jsp\">Alaska.org</a>.</li> </ul> <ul> <li>Head over to this page from eHow.com for a brief overview of <a href=\"http://www.ehow.com/facts_7272807_do-pack-alaska-vacation_.html\">what items to pack</a> for your Alaskan vacation.</li> </ul>\n<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/244612/medium/244612.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n</p><ul> <li> Check out this page from <a href=\"http://www.sitka.net/sitka/culturehistory.html\">Sitka.net</a> to learn more about the history of this beautiful Alaskan city.</li> </ul> <ul> </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Lodge\'>Alaska Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge\'>Talon Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/244601/2011/09/30/if-our-blogs-have-piqued-your-interest-then-here-are-five-more-resources-to-boost-your-knowledge.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','If our blogs have piqued your interest, then here are five more resources to boost your knowledge.','Are you planning an Alaskan adventure? Do you want more tips on what to look for in a resort? You can find more helpful information on the following websites. To learn even more, contact Talon Lodge today at (888) 763-5630!  Visit this page from USATod...','publish','closed','closed','','if-our-blogs-have-piqued-your-interest-then-here-are-five-more-resources-to-boost-your-knowledge','','','2011-09-29 18:58:03','2011-09-29 18:58:03','',0,'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/244601/2011/09/30/if-our-blogs-have-piqued-your-interest-then-here-are-five-more-resources-to-boost-your-knowledge.html',0,'post','',0),(88,4,'2011-09-23 08:11:54','2011-09-23 08:11:54','<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/238452/medium/238452.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n</p><p>Alaska is one of the country&rsquo;s most beautiful and unique states. That&rsquo;s why so many people choose it as their vacation destination. <strong><a href=\"http://www.ehow.com/facts_7272807_do-pack-alaska-vacation_.html\"  title=\"Alaskan Fishing Resorts\">Alaskan fishing resorts</a></strong> can provide the best experience, offering luxury, style, and great outdoor opportunities. If you&rsquo;re planning an Alaskan vacation, then look for these qualities in a resort:</p> <ul> <li><strong>Included Meals</strong></li> </ul> <p>Some fishing resorts are home to stunning restaurants that provide delicious meals&mdash;but at an outrageous price! When looking for a true luxury experience, you should find a resort that includes meals with each guests&rsquo; stay. This feature lets you experience a variety of delectable, top-quality meals for breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Many resorts offer an assortment of gourmet seafood entr&eacute;es, featuring favorites such as salmon, crab, and halibut.</p> <ul> <li><strong>Guided Activities</strong></li> </ul> <p>Many Alaskan visitors want to spend time outdoors during their vacation. Look for a resort that offers guided fishing, hiking, and kayaking tours and activities. Whether you prefer the water or the land, you&rsquo;ll be able to experience a true adventure on your <strong><a href=\"http://www.sitka.net/sitka/culturehistory.html\"  title=\"Alaskan Vacation\">Alaskan vacation</a></strong>.</p> <ul> <li><strong>A Relaxing Atmosphere</strong></li> </ul> <p>After experiencing the outdoors, you&rsquo;ll want to have a comfortable place to rest. You can find this comfort in a resort where guests are treated as a top priority. These resorts offer the best in relaxation, simplicity, and caring treatment. They also offer open, spacious rooms that let you clear your mind and enjoy every moment of your vacation.</p> <ul> <li><strong>An On-Site Spa</strong></li> </ul> <p>Nothing provides more relaxation that a trip to the spa. Some Alaskan fishing resorts offer on-site spas where guests can choose from a variety of styles of massage therapy. The experience is made even more relaxing and serene by the beautiful views all around you.</p> <p>You&rsquo;ll find all of these great features and more at <strong><a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a></strong>. Our luxury Alaskan fishing resort provides everything you need for fun, adventure, and total relaxation. For more information about our resort, visit our website or <strong><a href=\"http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/contact\"  title=\"Contact Talon Lodge\">contact us</a></strong> at (888) 763-5630.</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Fishing\'>Fishing</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Lodge\'>Alaska Fishing Lodge</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/238451/2011/09/23/what-to-look-for-in-an-alaskan-fishing-resort.html#comments\'>0 comments</a> | <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/238451/2011/09/23/what-to-look-for-in-an-alaskan-fishing-resort.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','What to Look for in an Alaskan Fishing Resort','\n\nAlaska is one of the country&rsquo;s most beautiful and unique states. That&rsquo;s why so many people choose it as their vacation destination. Alaskan fishing resorts can provide the best experience, offering luxury, style, and great outdoor opportu...','inherit','open','open','','75-revision','','','2011-09-23 08:11:54','2011-09-23 08:11:54','',75,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=88',0,'revision','',0),(89,4,'2011-09-16 14:36:47','2011-09-16 14:36:47','<p class=\"videos\">\n<a href=\'http://www.youtube.com/v/5yRwf5W_beY?hl=en&fs=1\'>http://www.youtube.com/v/5yRwf5W_beY?hl=en&fs=1</a>\n</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.co