odge.com/about/location.asp\"  title=\"Sitka\">Sitka</a></strong> is one of Alaska&rsquo;s most beautiful cities. Sitting on the edge of the Pacific Ocean, it&rsquo;s often called the &ldquo;Paris of the Pacific.&rdquo; Just 800 miles north of Seattle, this wonderful city is home to some of the world&rsquo;s best whale-watching.</p> <p>In this video, you&rsquo;ll get a closer look at the beautiful city of Sitka. Every year, people come from around the world to get amazing views of humpback whales that travel through the waters of Sitka. The mountains extend out to the waters, offering some of the world&rsquo;s most unique views.</p> <p>If you&rsquo;re ready to experience Sitka, then visit us at <strong><a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a></strong>! Our luxury fishing resort is the best way to experience our wonderful city and explore the beauty of Alaska. Visit our website or <strong><a href=\"http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/contact\"  title=\"Contact Talon Lodge\">contact us</a></strong> at (888) 763-5630.</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Video\'>Video</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska+Fishing+Sitka\'>Alaska Fishing Sitka</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Sitka\'>Sitka</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Sitka+Fishing+Lodges\'>Sitka Fishing Lodges</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaska\'>Alaska</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/232993/2011/09/16/video-post-card---bob-marshall-wilderness-award.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','Video Post Card - Bob Marshall Wilderness Award','\nhttp://www.youtube.com/v/5yRwf5W_beY?hl=en&amp;fs=1\nSitka is one of Alaska&rsquo;s most beautiful cities. Sitting on the edge of the Pacific Ocean, it&rsquo;s often called the &ldquo;Paris of the Pacific.&rdquo; Just 800 miles north of Seattle, this wonde...','inherit','open','open','','76-revision-3','','','2011-09-16 14:36:47','2011-09-16 14:36:47','',76,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=103',0,'revision','',0),(104,4,'2011-09-09 18:40:26','2011-09-09 18:40:26','<p>It may be located in the largest state, but Sitka seems to be Alaska&rsquo;s best kept secret. This beautiful city, with a population under 9,000 residents, offers some of the state&rsquo;s most beautiful views. Sitka is also home to some of <strong><a href=\"http://traveltips.usatoday.com/information-hiking-alaska-10168.html\"  title=\"Alaska\'s Top Fishing Lodges\">Alaska&rsquo;s top fishing lodges</a></strong>, offering tourists stunning hiking and kayaking opportunities. These tips will help you plan your adventures:</p> <ul> <li><strong>Ask about hiking and kayaking guides.</strong> </li> </ul> <p>Alaskan fishing lodges don&rsquo;t just give you access to great land, great waters, and great fish; they also give you the tools you need to make the most of your experience. Ask the staff about guides or scheduled trips. They can plan a day of hiking for you and provide you with information on where to go and what you&rsquo;ll see there. An experienced captain can help you find your way through the majestic waters.</p> <ul> <li><strong>Dress appropriately.</strong></li> </ul> <p>It&rsquo;s important to wear the right type and amount of clothing when hiking in Alaska. You can prepare yourself for the weather by adding layers. Start with long underwear, followed by warm, water-resistant pants and a sweater, topped with a warm winter jacket. Find lightweight hikers or hiking boots to keep your feet more comfortable during the hike.</p> <ul> <li><strong>Bring a camera!</strong></li> </ul> <p>After your hiking or kayaking adventure is planned, you&rsquo;ll want to make sure to pack your camera. The scenery of Sitka is sure to leave you breathless. While the views are unforgettable, a camera will help you share your <strong><a href=\"http://www.sitka.org/explore/wildlife/\"  title=\"Alaskan Vacation\">Alaskan vacation</a></strong> adventures with your loved ones back home and bring you long-lasting memories. When you stop to take a break during your hike, grab your camera and take a few pictures for keepsakes!</p> <p>At <strong><a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a></strong>, we offer the best luxury fishing in Sitka. Our gorgeous resort lets you rest in style, and our professional captains and hiking guides will help you make the most of your experience. Learn more today by visiting our website or <strong><a href=\"http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/contact\"  title=\"Contact Talon Lodge\">contacting us</a></strong> at (888) 763-5630.</p>\n<p class=\"photos\">\n<img src=\'http://rc-images.s3.amazonaws.com/7f6a3dc1-3465-493f-80e6-ab1f4a9be23d/media/227158/medium/227158.PNG?gen=1\' /><br />\n</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Hiking\'>Hiking</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Luxury+Alaskan+Fishing+Lodge\'>Luxury Alaskan Fishing Lodge</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Kayaking\'>Kayaking</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Alaskan+Vacations\'>Alaskan Vacations</a></p>\n<a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/227069/2011/09/09/tips-for-hiking-and-kayaking-adventures-in-alaska.html?commentFocus=true#comments\'>Leave a comment &raquo;</a>\n<br />','Tips for Hiking and Kayaking Adventures in Alaska','It may be located in the largest state, but Sitka seems to be Alaska&rsquo;s best kept secret. This beautiful city, with a population under 9,000 residents, offers some of the state&rsquo;s most beautiful views. Sitka is also home to some of Alaska&amp;rsq...','inherit','open','open','','77-revision-3','','','2011-09-09 18:40:26','2011-09-09 18:40:26','',77,'http://wordpress.talonlodge.com/?p=104',0,'revision','',0),(105,4,'2011-09-02 06:52:43','2011-09-02 06:52:43','<p>The Talon Lodge is absolutely first-rate. It\'s situated on an island off the coast of Sitka, and it\'s one of the most beautiful settings I\'ve ever witnessed. The views are simply stunning. And the grounds are meticulously maintained.<br /><br />Owners Phil and Gwen are on-site, totally commited, and very approachable. Their hand-picked staff is extraordinary and provides excellent service.<br /><br />The food -- prepared by highly trained chefs and paired with excellent wines -- is top notch. And the bars (one indoors and one on the patio) are fully stocked.<br /><br />Rooms are very spacious, well-appointed, and offer amazing views.<br /><br />And the fishing? Well, it\'s about as good as it gets. The guides and boat captains know the local waters well,<br /><br />If you\'re looking for the perfect Alaskan getaway, look no further than the Talon Lodge.</p>\n<p>Rated 5 out of 5 stars</p>\n<p><a href=\'http://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g60966-d1553334-r117515611-Talon_Lodge_Spa-Sitka_Alaska.html\'>Reviewed on TripAdvisor at 8/22/11</a></p>\n<p>Reviewed by <a href=\'http://www.tripadvisor.com/members/PaulJamesTulsa\'>PaulJamesTulsa</a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.talonlodge.com/\"  title=\"Talon Lodge\">Talon Lodge</a>&nbsp;is a luxury fishing lodge located in Sitka, Alaska. For more information about us or to make a reservation, visit our website or call&nbsp;(888) 763-5630&nbsp;today!</p>\n<p class=\"tags\">More from Talon Lodge Blog: <a href=\'http://www.luxuryalaskanfishinglodge.com/search/tag/Talon+Lodge+Reviews\'>Talon Lodge Reviews</a>, <a href=\'http://www.luxu